text: Shoot-Out at Medicine Bend is a 1957 American western movie directed by Richard L. Bare and starring Randolph Scott, James Craig, Angie Dickinson, James Garner, Trevor Bardette, Myron Healey, John Alderson, Don Beddoe. It was distributed by Warner Bros.. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1957 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Warner Bros. movies
